kun reading compounds: 鼈【すっぽん】Chinese soft-shelled turtle (Pelodiscus sinensis), soft-shelled turtle (Trionychidae), trap door located on the walkway in a kabuki theatre, bilge pump (used on traditional Japanese ships)
鼈茸【すっぽんたけ】common stinkhorn (Phallus impudicus)
月とスッポン【つきとスッポン】two things that superficially similar but completely different, night and day, chalk and cheese, the Moon and a turtle
